{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you like the game please don't forget to add it to your wishlist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326040/extras/addtowishlist_gif.gif?t=1732102529\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wendigo Hunter</strong> is an action roguelite dungeon crawler with mysterious atmosphere and minimalistic visual. As a chosen member of a cult you will try to hunt down a mythological creature hiding deep in dungeons and abandoned ruins. Unleash a captivating journey where fallen enemies' souls become the key to unlocking mesmerizing magical skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fight, collect, upgrade, die, try again...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326040/extras/SteamGif.gif?t=1732102529\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> master your fighting skills in combat with various creatures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> explore randomly generated dungeon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> upgrade your magical skills by collecting souls of dead enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> gain permanent upgrades by spending collected gems</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you succeed or the next hunter from the cult will need to be chosen?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ABOUT DEVELOPER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Peter Jurkovsk\u00fd, solo developer and father of 1, began work on Wendigo Hunter as a hobby in 2022 after releasing his first PC game called Juro Janosik.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2326040/extras/FPU_ENG_WHITE